@startuml
title InsightsRadar v1 - Digest Failover and Triage

participant "Worker Queue Consumer" as Digest
participant "Workers AI Primary" as Primary
participant "Workers AI Fallback" as Fallback
database "D1 Metadata DB" as D1
actor Operator
participant "Worker API\n/admin/reprocess" as API
queue "Cloudflare Queue" as Q

Digest -> Primary: attempt 1..3
alt primary succeeds
  Primary --> Digest: valid schema payload
  Digest -> D1: status=processed
else primary exhausted
  Digest -> Fallback: attempt 1..3
  alt fallback succeeds
    Fallback --> Digest: valid schema payload
    Digest -> D1: status=processed\nmodel_used_final=fallback
  else fallback exhausted
    Fallback --> Digest: failures
    Digest -> D1: status=digest_failed\nfailure_reason + retry_count + attempts trace
  end
end

== Triage ==
Operator -> D1: inspect failed record fields
Operator -> API: manual reprocess request
API -> Q: enqueue manual_reprocess
Q -> Digest: re-run digest pipeline

@enduml
